  "instructions": [
    "combine rice mix and water in a large bowl and let soak for 30 minutes.",
    "heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add garlic and saut\u00177e until fragrant.",
    "add mackerel fillets and cook until lightly browned on both sides.",
    "transfer the mackerel to a bamboo steamer and place over boiling water.",
    "add green onions, parsley, lemon juice, sumac, cumin, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and saut\u00177e until the onions are tender.",
    "place the steamer over the skillet and cover with a lid.",
    "steam for 15-20 minutes or until the fish is cooked through.",
    "serve the fish on top of the rice mixture.",
    "garnish with additional parsley and green onions if desired."
